<p>This chart displays the peak-to-trough drawdown of your portfolio's equity throughout the backtest period. The drawdown of each day is defined as the percentage loss since the maximum equity value before the current day. The drawdowns are calculated based on daily data. The top 5 drawdown periods are marked in the chart with different colors.</p>